Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.22,0:00:02.02,Black Signs 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Staff Room
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.81,0:00:02.02,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:09.36,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's my bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:11.53,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:14.07,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,What was that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:53.96,Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,500)}Overlap
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:00.09,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:01.51,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,This is the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:04.26,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,You two were found\Ncollapsed by the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:05.72,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:07.73,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Did you miss your step?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:09.27,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:11.94,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I sorta slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:15.78,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-kun, you shielded \NKariu-san from the fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:16.69,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Nicely done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:18.61,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:21.70,Blue Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}* Actually 27
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.16,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:26.04,Italics Dialogue,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Inukai-sensei, Inukai-sensei, \Nplease come to the staff room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:28.12,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:32.33,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back in a minute. \NCan you stay with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:33.75,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:34.84,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:38.42,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Your classmate, Hishiro-san, let us know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:41.51,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,She carried your stuff here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:43.89,Main Dialogue,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Thank her later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.56,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hishiro-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:54.27,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it... that was Hishiro-san's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:57.19,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Kariu have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:02:59.70,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What was she trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:04.53,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0000,0000,0000,,She's got top sales again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:08.16,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0000,0000,0000,,We'll lose face if we let\Na woman trounce us like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:11.17,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't she just quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:13.17,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0000,0000,0000,,Hasn't she worked it out yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:15.96,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0000,0000,0000,,With all we've done? She knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.80,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off. The new guy's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:19.88,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.47,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0000,0000,0000,,She's in charge of his training, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:25.35,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rat us out, Kaizaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:29.60,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.81,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make absolutely sure \Nnothing like this happens again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:35.02,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let us make it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:40.36,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You know this mess wasn't your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:43.07,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,We went over the order several times
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:46.16,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,while you were showing me the ropes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:47.03,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Someone must've...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:47.79,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:53.25,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it make you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:57.50,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0000,0000,0000,,Knocking others down to gain an advantage\Nis a fruitless endeavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:02.42,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0000,0000,0000,,It means they've given up \Non winning any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:05.26,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0000,0000,0000,,At first,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:09.60,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0000,0000,0000,,we all competed fair and square. \NIt was really fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.10,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0000,0000,0000,,But then,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:15.98,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0000,0000,0000,,somehow we went from rivals to enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:23.45,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing hard workers turn out \Nlike that doesn't make me mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:24.78,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0000,0000,0000,,Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:26.24,Flashback Dialogue,Michiru,0000,0000,0000,,...very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.12,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Were you trying to bully her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:32.62,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,A hard worker like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:37.25,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Are you awake, Kariu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:43.17,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no sudden movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:48.72,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, Hishiro-san found us\Nand let the teachers know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:52.93,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure she took that \Ngreen bag home with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.44,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,That bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:01.11,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It was Hishiro-san's, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:03.36,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:12.24,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.20,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Kariu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.04,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You steal anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:18.04,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:20.17,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:24.26,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to trouble her a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:28.22,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I was gonna hide it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:29.64,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:32.89,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:36.73,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Have you given up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:39.90,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think harassing her is\Nthe only way you'll beat her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.19,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:48.78,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna tell her I tried to\Nharass her because I was jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.74,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You're close to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:54.08,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you knew it was her bag,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:56.87,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,and that's why you're mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:06:01.42,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I bet I could hurt you more if I told Oga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:03.46,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.67,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:08.55,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But... that is what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:13.22,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to knock others down a peg\N just means lowering yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:18.60,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go trampling all the hard work \Nand trust you've built up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:21.23,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It insults the effort you put in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:24.11,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,The only way that would make you happy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:28.11,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,is if you were a loser \Nwho'd given up on trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:32.87,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think that describes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:36.45,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,The Kariu I know hates losing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:38.75,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,is curt but kind,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.87,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,and is a hard worker with a strong heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:44.92,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Because I know how hard you've worked,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:48.09,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really mad. Just very, very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:53.01,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act like some filthy adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.47,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You're still young!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:56.64,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up on try—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:57.73,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,What would you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.89,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you lecturing me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.06,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,We're the same age!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.44,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}did{\i0} try!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:03.86,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:07.28,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, they don't \Neven see me as a rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:10.53,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Honoka for sports, Hishiro for studies...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.28,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying desperately to beat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.53,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,So why do they act like\NI'm no threat at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.49,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I the only one with problems?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:20.08,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I try and try and try and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:39.18,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard I try,\N I get nothing in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:41.23,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,It's all pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.69,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:46.77,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You're just too busy comparing \Nyourself to others to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:49.11,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Those comparisons aren't the only measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:52.78,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it's all pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:57.08,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You've worked hard and made yourself better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.79,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you got in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.37,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,So don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.83,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,...put yourself down like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:06.71,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:08.46,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:15.30,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,...all my hard work...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:19.14,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,...wasn't pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:24.27,Black Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Nurse's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:26.65,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.23,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.23,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Always gotta act tough, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:33.49,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You said no matter how hard you tried...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:35.28,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.60,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But Hishiro-san's trying, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:41.66,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,She was in the staff room this late...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:45.21,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she had questions \Nfor the teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:48.13,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,There are things even she doesn't find easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.63,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,She's really awkward, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:57.22,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I think you've got the \Nwrong idea about her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:59.43,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You've never really talked to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:01.27,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:05.14,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Next time you get a chance, \Nask her to smile for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:06.94,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:08.73,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:14.15,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I just lectured her like an old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:17.03,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up on trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:19.74,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about pot calling the kettle black.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:23.54,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one to talk,\Nconsidering I gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.88,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's up, Hishiro-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:36.22,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:39.76,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,There's something bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:43.27,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about it didn't get me anywhere,\Nso I waited to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:48.27,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Kariu-san have my bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:51.48,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought about it a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:56.11,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,but all I can think of is that \Nshe stole it, so I'm confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.24,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:01.74,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu-san and my eyes \Nhave been meeting often lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:04.54,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,and every time, I've made sure to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:08.25,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought we were friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:11.21,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Think!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:16.05,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell should I tell this \Nmalice-free tone-deaf communicator?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:24.06,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She thought it was dangerous \Nto leave the bag lying in the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:27.52,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,So she thought she'd take care of it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.31,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:33.11,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.07,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I know the reason,\NI feel a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:39.53,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I knew she couldn't have tried to steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:44.24,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't think of anything else.\NI'm ashamed of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:52.00,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Is getting rid of all the thorns in\Nsomeone's path really what's best for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:55.00,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.30,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,That was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:03.60,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu took your bag to\Ncause problems for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:06.14,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why would she...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:09.02,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted the silver pin,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:11.40,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,so she was jealous and frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:15.11,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu-san wants this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:16.53,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Holy crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:17.99,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,She's even denser than Oga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:21.49,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Then if I give her this,\N can we be friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:22.49,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.41,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:29.66,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Does Kariu-san hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:32.46,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess you wouldn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:35.79,Flashback Dialogue,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,Hishiro-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:39.92,Flashback Dialogue,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,for someone so smart,\N you can be really dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.43,Flashback Dialogue,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't noticed that\Neveryone's mad at you, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:49.39,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what I say \Nthat makes people so mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:52.31,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand how they feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:56.44,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I know that's because \NI haven't properly socialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:58.53,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've tried to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:01.45,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've tried to study up on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.61,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,but I just don't know what's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:06.87,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:10.04,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,There is no right answer for getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:13.00,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Different people require different answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:17.84,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Different people... \Nrequire different answers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.01,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I didn't mean to overload you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:25.26,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wait for Kariu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:27.93,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave this be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:31.35,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be her friend for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:34.27,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know how.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:38.40,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't know the right answer... \NI'll just ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:42.07,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Like you're asking a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.78,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,One more question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:49.83,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw your hands wrapped \Nprotectively around her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:52.16,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,why did I feel a pang?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:55.00,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:59.00,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's ineffective to deal \Nwith many problems at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.42,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,One at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.09,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:07.93,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I think I have to take care of this myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:09.43,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,G-Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:11.47,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:24.82,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:27.82,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Like I can possibly just leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.28,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Will she be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.99,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno, will she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.29,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:36.71,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You should be used to this by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:39.71,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever you go, I go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:40.67,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:42.38,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your voice down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:43.92,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,And don't be mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:48.05,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to be \Nwatching me, not Hishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:53.02,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,The influence your choices \Nhave on those around you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:57.19,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,is also a target of my observations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:03.90,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:05.15,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.41,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,An ambush?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:17.04,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:20.17,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,She knows I had her bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.00,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,So this is an interrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:24.71,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:28.34,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want this silver pin that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:31.01,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Right for the jugular!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:36.23,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you tried to run off with my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:37.85,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-san told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:38.69,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,That jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:41.02,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,She ratted me out for ratting Kariu out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:44.27,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,When I asked why you would do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:46.40,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,he said your motive was this silver pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:49.78,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,So I asked if we could \Nbe friends if I gave you this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:51.99,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,and he said no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:54.28,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:57.20,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.46,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:03.46,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:04.42,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:06.38,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you take my bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:09.88,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do that \Nto someone you don't hate?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.89,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,She straight up asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:15.14,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno how she can keep asking this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:17.35,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it hurt her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.39,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it {\i1}is{\i0} Hishiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:21.40,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.19,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:24.65,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Answer, Kariu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:29.28,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:31.49,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,...running anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:33.57,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:36.66,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard I try, I can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:39.71,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,You took what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:42.21,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,You stood where I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:43.95,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,And ever since you won, you've always,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:47.63,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,always flashed that mocking smile,\N so of course I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:59.10,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've never mocked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:01.64,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,You do! Every time our eyes meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:02.27,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:02.77,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,You do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.90,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I ever do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:06.82,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.03,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,How can you deny it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:11.20,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,That constant stream of sneers...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:14.37,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Every time our eyes meet, \Nevery time we speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:18.62,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Next time you get a chance, \Nask her to smile for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:20.91,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:23.62,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Hishiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.96,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Smile for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:29.51,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.51,0:16:33.93,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. I'm trying to think \Nof a reason I'd mock—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:35.01,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:38.26,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,A normal smile, like you'd do \Nif your eyes met someone's!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:44.14,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.78,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,You just freaked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:50.57,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:53.20,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Er... wait... let me get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:54.91,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.70,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Hishiro thinks that's a smile?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:59.58,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,She was trying for a friendly smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:03.08,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Kaizaki was lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:06.00,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Smile again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:08.71,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:10.63,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:15.22,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my god, you suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.18,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,How is that a smile?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.60,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Have you even looked in a mirror?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:21.93,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea\Nhow it makes people feel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:24.69,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were \Nmocking me this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:29.90,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I have been smiling in the hope \Nthat we could be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.37,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:44.66,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,How awkward can you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:49.38,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,My strong point is I'm smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:52.92,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't understand something,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:56.93,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I look into it on my own, \Nand if I still don't get it, I ask until I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:18:00.68,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,My weak point is that \NI'm not interested in other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.47,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,She said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:06.39,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, I don't know \Nhow to interact with anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:09.40,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,and I must have caused \Nlots of problems for people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:13.94,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, I'm trying to change myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:18.32,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu-san, that's who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:22.24,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,But would you be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:29.21,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,It's my pleasure, Hishiro Chizuru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.17,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,That day,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:35.63,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,she wasn't intentionally \Nignoring the handshake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:45.35,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Hishiro Chizuru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:51.56,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,But in return, recognize me as your rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:52.61,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:55.99,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely take that silver pin from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:59.32,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it, you can have it next test...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:02.16,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare! I want it, but not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:04.62,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,If you hold back, we're not friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:07.50,Not Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Not Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:07.50,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:12.25,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:13.42,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.05,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.17,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:23.68,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:30.69,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, so you can actually smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.44,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,But I smile all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:33.52,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.90,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You told Hishiro about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:42.78,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:46.08,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you take a picture for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:49.50,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,A test subject grinning \Nbecause a high school girl LIMEd him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:50.53,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,For my report.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:51.54,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Delete it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:53.54,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we drinking at my place, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:54.42,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What is all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:56.25,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:59.92,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You helped them become friends.\NLet's celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.34,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,We've got school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:06.26,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,For an ex-NEET, you sure are serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:08.06,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Not NEET! I was a part-timer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:11.27,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yoake-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:15.56,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Was what I told Kariu\N really the right thing to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:18.57,Black Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}{\an5}Resignation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:20.90,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,In reality, I couldn't grow up, \Nand became a NEET.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:25.57,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,And those awful bullies probably \Nstill have their jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:29.75,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I know the real truth is uglier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:34.17,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it wasn't the ugly truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:35.88,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,But it wasn't a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:39.42,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It's what you really meant, \Nso isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:43.38,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,When she's out in the \Nreal world and stumbles,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:48.43,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,she'll remember someone \Nyelling at her, if not who.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:53.31,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I think what happened today \Nwill stay with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:55.73,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:21:00.15,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Though, really, it was \Nthe pot calling the kettle black!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:03.24,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Yelling at her for comparing \Nherself to others!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:07.57,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Says the man so worried about appearances, \Nhe pretended he still had a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:10.58,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I thought the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:12.58,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,So? Are you liking ReLIFE?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:17.17,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Is it letting you take a long,\Nhard look at yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:23.59,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,The way you see through everything \Nis seriously driving me nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.76,0:22:48.68,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Rena, see any empty seats?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:52.55,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Honoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:56.89,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:02.19,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't mind eating lunch with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:05.03,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:06.61,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I like being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:08.70,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:09.74,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to change?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:11.95,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.74,0:23:15.33,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Then, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.33,0:23:16.49,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.49,0:23:18.16,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't thank me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:19.71,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:21.29,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,This is normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:40.14,Next Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:28.09,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hishiro, you need to first\Npractice how to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:28.84,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Grin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:30.05,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:31.76,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought I was doing it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.76,0:23:33.76,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me how it's done, Kariu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:36.02,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:40.14,Next Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1200,1)}This Isn't the First Time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:36.68,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:37.64,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:39.52,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna hear that from you!
